{"questionId": "608eeb6e", "correctAnswer": "C", "section": "Math", "steps": [{"title": "Solve the system by substitution", "content": "From $5x=15$, $x=3$. Substitute into $-4x+y=-2$: $-12+y=-2$, so $y=10$."}, {"title": "Find the value of $x + y$", "content": "Then $x+y=3+10=13$. That matches choice <strong>C</strong> — <strong>C</strong> is correct.", "desmosExpressions": ["x = 3", "y = 4x - 2"]}]}